.TH snmpa_mib_data 3 "snmp 5.20.1" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
snmpa_mib_data \- Behaviour module for the SNMP agent mib-server data module.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
